name: Royally Rockin Round Queen
description: I want to bring you on a journey. Will you join me? To see the best music in town be you a Rock n Roller, Jazz connoisseur, Country hoedowner or anything in between you will see the best music Toronto has to offer and you'll have one special time doing it. Don't hesitate. A magical night awaits you. Open up your mind, body, soul and ears and join me.
